headline: Traditional Bank Chooses Jack Henry for Modern, Open Technology Platform
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that Traditional Bank has selected Jack Henry to strengthen its technology framework, elevate employee and customer experiences, and enable continued growth.
